Unfortunately, due to our relatively poor relations with the Liberal Party, the Liberals are demanding that we guarantee them a number of compromises, seeking to rein in our socialist policies. We will need to accept at least some of them.

@lib_menu

The Liberals have indicated a series of demands.

- @no_nationalise: We will refrain from undertaking a policy of nationalisations.
- @yes_nationalise: Drop our promise against nationalisations.
- @no_works: We will guarantee to only carry out minor public works programmes to avoid deficit spending.
- @yes_works: Drop our promise against going into deficit spending on public works.
- @free_trade: We will commit to a policy of free trade.
- @no_free_trade: Drop our promise to uphold free trade.
- @no_taxes: We will promise not to raise taxes on the highest earners.
- @yes_taxes: Drop our promise not to raise taxes on the highest earners.
- @enough: That should be enough, let's negotiate the ministries.
- @lib_no_gov: The government cannot be formed.

